   Height 3
   Speed 30
   Damage 0
   PROJECTILE
   +DONTREFLECT
   +SKYEXPLODE
   RENDERSTYLE ADD
   Alpha 1.0
   States
   {
  Spawn:
	TNT1 A 0 A_JumpIfInTargetInventory ("VanillaItem", 1, "VanillaLoop")
	TNT1 A 0 A_JumpIfInTargetInventory ("BlueItem", 1, "BlueLoop")
